name: heat-related-deaths-among-california-residents-may-september-2000-2009
notes: This dataset contains counts, rates, and confidence intervals of heat-related deaths among California residents for the years 2000-2009. These data are stratified by year, age group, race/ethnicity and gender. Crude and age-adjusted rates and confidence intervals are included.
